-- Libyan Central Bank Is `Extremely Satistifed' With UniCredit Investment
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-09-20T10:20:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/libyan-central-bank-is-extremely-satistifed-with-unicredit-investment.html

          
          
             The Central Bank of Libya is
“extremely satisfied” with its investment in UniCredit SpA,
according to an e-mailed statement today.  
 The bank is also “extremely satisfied” with its
relationship with Italian regulatory authorities, the statement
said. The central bank is an “independent” instituion and the
majority of its board members are independent, according to
statement.  
          
          


  


        